[B][SIZE="5"]FEATURES[/SIZE][/B]
Layers
Battery bar
LCD denisty options
Multi-window
Status bar customization
Quick setting customization
Quick setting pull down options
Force expand notifications
Time context headers in panel
DarkUI switch
Advanced power menu
Extra IME options
Lockscreen shortcuts
Animations
    -Power menu
    -List view
    -System
    -Toast
Navbar customization:
    -Navbar button color
    -Slim-Dim
    -Navbar DPI
    -DT2S on Navbar
 Buttons settings:
    -Long-press/double-tap actions
    -Volume rocker   
More to come, we are never done...

[B][SIZE="5"][COLOR="red"][URL="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DMCYosPotf8Q0RmtNbpNipr2ib0u2keBICUIX-J6m6k"]CHANGELOG[/URL][/COLOR][/SIZE][/B]

[SIZE="3"][B]Steps:[/B][/SIZE]

[B][U]Coming from another rom[/U][/B]
1) Download CandySiX.zip
2) Download 6.0 Gapps (optional)
3) Boot into recovery (either twrp or cwm)
4) Full wipe (Dalvik Cache, Cache, System, Factory Data Reset)
5) Flash CandySiX.zip 
6) Flash Gapps
7) Reboot

[B][U]Updating from previous CandySiX release[/U][/B]
1) Download CandySiX.zip
2) Boot into recovery
3) Flash CandySiX.zip
4) Reboot

